import React from 'react'
import {Container,Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap'
import { BreadCrumb } from '../components/BreadCrumb/BreadCrumb.comp'

export const TicketList = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Row>
            <Col>
            <BreadCrumb page="TicketList"></BreadCrumb> 
            </Col>
        </Row>

    </Container>
  )
}
